reviewText: The Angels of God are always with you. Take a moment, in complete silence, to know that they are with you. Every one have an Guardian Angel. To help you, to guide in your life each day, to guide you to God! To guide to Heaven for all the eternity! God give you a Guardian Angel, to you! And in this picture you can see that. That reflect the love of God. If you talk with God, with His Angels, all can be better, all can be perfect, beautiful... As happened in this wonderful picture.
It was very interesting. They were true stories. It was what I expected, and I would definitely buy this again.
